<% layout("/layouts/boilerplate") %>

<div class="container my-5">
  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-md-8">
      <h2 class="fw-bold mb-4">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved text-danger me-2"></i>Privacy Policy
      </h2>

      <p class="text-muted">Last updated: July 2026</p>

      <p class="lead text-secondary">
        At StayNest, we respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect information when you use our accommodation booking platform.
      </p>

      <hr class="my-4">

      <h4 class="fw-bold">Information We Collect</h4>
      <p class="text-secondary">
        We collect information required for account creation, authentication, property listings, bookings, reviews, and communication with our support team. Uploaded images are securely stored using cloud-based media services.
      </p>

      <h4 class="fw-bold mt-4">Account Security</h4>
      <p class="text-secondary">
        User passwords are securely encrypted through authentication systems. We use secure sessions to protect user accounts and prevent unauthorized access.
      </p>

      <h4 class="fw-bold mt-4">Bookings and Payments</h4>
      <p class="text-secondary mb-5">
        Booking details and payment-related information are processed securely through trusted payment providers. StayNest does not store sensitive payment card information.
      </p>

      <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-dark px-4 py-2 rounded-3">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left me-2"></i>Back to Home
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>